core-task.name: cacheBust
core-task.info: Bust static assets from the cache using content hashing

core-task.name: cachebreak
core-task.info: Busts cache based on its MD5Hash

core-task.name: config
core-task.info: sets up all the configurations needed for tasks to run

core-task.name: fetch-dependencies
core-task.info: Checks js/app-name.json file, and if any of the entries are URLs , it fetches the JavaScript file, saves it in the js/lib directory, and changes the entry in ap-name.json file to point to location of file in lib

core-task.name: setup
core-task.info: Checks that all the required configuration files are present for building this project

core-task.name: update-dependency-json
core-task.info: Writes back the latest dependency json to js/app-name.json file

core-task.name: watch
core-task.info: Run predefined tasks whenever watched files change.
